</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        Initial clone:<br />
        <pre><code>git clone git://github.com/chyrp/chyrp.git</code></pre>
    </li>
    <li>
        Stay updated:<br />
        <pre><code>git pull # and then run upgrade.php</code></pre>
    </li>
</ul>
